{
  "stem": "22391.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't care about anything else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I picked up that sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I started to make some shirts from sheets for my husband and for the other friends.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I made a skirt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't even-- no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, I made a skirt for myself and a blouse, so I could change clothes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was very happy with this stupid sewing machine over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I started to work right away to do something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they took us also with a truck to the station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at the station we, we went by train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we were supposed to go from there to Bamberg, to more like a civilian place to be, and not in the camp now.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But somehow, all guys who are hungry, but I don't know what they did wrong.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We was staying in a-- Abe going to tell you the rest of it-- in a place where the trains were.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they saw the American train was coming in with food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had conserves on it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had peaches and pears in, in big can.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they started to steal some, because they were hungry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we got punished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were sent to another camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "From there we went to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we stayed there for a while, until we got transported into Landsberg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a whole big thing, but he remembers more dates and everything than I do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was a displaced person camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we were there already we, we got used to, to our troubles, and we know we have no place to go.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just have to do whatever we could do for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was-- first I started to make a kosher kitchen where we could eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
